data.description: Charming one-level home, boasting timeless all-brick construction. Situated on a spacious lot, this property offers both style and functionality. Enjoy outdoor living on the deck, surrounded by nature. The house features new pipes installed underneath just 2 years ago, offering peace of mind with a 20-year warranty. Freshly painted interiors complement the gleaming hardwood floors, creating a warm ambiance throughout. Convenience is key with a one-car garage. Don't miss this opportunity to own a meticulously maintained home in a prime location.
